  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "我们熟悉的 1、x、x 平方，虽然能拼出任何多项式，却彼此纠缠不清。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "数学家想要一组更好的基：它们在某种意义下互相垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "在区间负一到正一上，这组正交的多项式，就叫勒让德多项式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "recur",
      "line_id": "rec-1",
      "filename": "recur-rec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/recur-rec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "它们从最简单的两项开始：P 零等于一，P 一等于 x。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "recur",
      "line_id": "rec-2",
      "filename": "recur-rec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/recur-rec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.68,
      "size": 58896,
      "text": "之后每一阶都由前两阶推出：n 加一乘 P n 加一，等于二 n 加一乘 x P n，减去 n 乘 P n 减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "recur",
      "line_id": "rec-3",
      "filename": "recur-rec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/recur-rec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "这条 Bonnet 递推，让我们无需积分就能稳稳地算出任意高阶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "ort-1",
      "filename": "ortho-ort-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/ortho-ort-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "把两条不同阶的曲线相乘，再在负一到正一上积分，结果恰好是零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "ort-2",
      "filename": "ortho-ort-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/ortho-ort-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "这正是正交的含义：不同阶之间没有任何重叠的分量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "ort-3",
      "filename": "ortho-ort-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/ortho-ort-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "右边的矩阵里，只有对角线亮着，其余格子都近乎为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "apply-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/apply-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "用它们的零点作节点，就得到精度极高的高斯-勒让德数值积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "apply-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/apply-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "在球面上,它们又长成球谐函数,描述电磁场与量子轨道。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "调整最高阶数，看曲线如何一条条叠加，振荡越来越丰富。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "同时留意正交矩阵：无论加到几阶，非对角始终保持为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "勒让德多项式由三项递推生成，在区间上两两正交。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "size": 38448,
      "text": "它是高斯求积和球谐分析的基石，把复杂函数拆成干净的分量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "legendre-polynomials",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/legendre-polynomials/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "一组正交的曲线，撑起了物理与计算的半边天，我们下次再见！"
    }
